K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-008:127b-1: a'arya pra daksh'a ratna tra y'a n'a ma dh'a ra n'i /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-008:127b-3: 'phags pa dkon mchog mchog gi rten la bskor ba bya ba'i gzungs zhes bya ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-008:127b-4: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh'akya thub pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-008:127b-5: aom na mod sha di ka [?] k'a la sarba ratna tra y'a ya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-008:127b-6: na ma ma pra daksha su pra daksh'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-008:127b-7: sarba p'a pam bi sho dha ni sv'ah'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-008:128a-1: lan gcig brjod pas phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal zhing bskor ba byas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-008:128a-2: thog ma med pa nas bsags pa'i sdig pa thams cad dag par 'gyur /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-008:128a-3: sangs rgyas kyi byang chub myur du thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-008:128a-5: bgegs kyis glags rnyed par mi 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-008:128a-7: gdon thams cad las thar bar 'gyur ro //
